isport.com/|accessdate=8 January 2014}}</ref>\n\n===Neftchi Baku Return===\nOn 11 September 2014, after being frozen out of the Gabala team, Allahverdiyev signed a two-year contract with [[Neftchi Baku PFC|Neftchi Baku]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Elnur Allahverdiyev: \"Neft\u00e7i\"nin u\u011furlar\u0131 \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn \u0259limd\u0259n g\u0259l\u0259ni ed\u0259c\u0259y\u0259m\"|url=http://www.neftchipfk.com/az/newsd.php?id=696|website=www.neftchipfk.com|publisher=[[Neftchi Baku PFC]]|accessdate=11 September 2014|language=Azerbaijani|date=11 September 2014}}</ref> After just four months with Neftchi, Allahverdiyev was released by the club in January 2015.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u041e\u0444\u0438\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e: \u0410\u043b\u043b\u0430\u0445\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0434\u0438\u0435\u0432\u0430 \u0432\u044b\u0433\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0438 \u0438\u0437 \u041d\u0435\u0444\u0442\u0447\u0438|url=http://www.azerifootball.com/ru/13/news/26431.html|website=azerifootball.com |publisher=Azerifootball|accessdate=7 January 2015|language=Russian|date=7 January 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|7 January 2015}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Soccerway Stats|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/elnur-allahverdiyev/35239/|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=20 September 2013}}</ref> \n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|[[Shafa Baku FK|Shafa Baku]]\n|[[2003\u201304 Azerbaijan Top League|2003\u201304]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Premier League Stats 2003/04 |url=http://www.pfl.az/upload/arxiv/200304/oyuncustats200304.pdf |publisher=Pe\u015f\u0259kar Futbol Liqas\u0131 |accessdate=17 September 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=http